</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/906cadd9f57172d2b5b0acf86cd199718630d4a5" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:13.533ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="{\displaystyle w(t)=w(-t)}"></span>;<br /></dd>
<dd>(b) non-increasing (for positive time): <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle w(t)\geq w(s)}">
