            <mi>j</mi>
            <mn>2</mn>
            <mi>&#x03C0;<!-- π --></mi>
            <mi>f</mi>
            <mi>&#x03C4;<!-- τ --></mi>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
        <mi>d</mi>
        <mi>&#x03C4;<!-- τ --></mi>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle X(t,f)=\int _{-\infty }^{\infty }w(t-\tau )x(\tau )e^{-j2\pi f\tau }d\tau }</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/f3c0eae04cf10d69d1e025b0727e5d4339c281a1" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.505ex; width:36.777ex; height:6.009ex;" alt="{\displaystyle X(t,f)=\int _{-\infty }^{\infty }w(t-\tau )x(\tau )e^{-j2\pi f\tau }d\tau }"></span></dd></dl>
<p>Converting into the discrete form:
</p>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle t=n\Delta _{t},f=m\Delta _{f},\tau =p\Delta _{t}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <mi>t</mi>
        <mo>=</mo>
        <mi>n</mi>
        <msub>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">&#x0394;<!-- Δ --></mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>t</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msub>
        <mo>,</mo>
        <mi>f</mi>
        <mo>=</mo>
        <mi>m</mi>
        <msub>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">&#x0394;<!-- Δ --></mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>f</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msub>
        <mo>,</mo>
        <mi>&#x03C4;<!-- τ --></mi>
        <mo>=</mo>
        <mi>p</mi>
        <msub>
          <mi mathvariant="normal">&#x0394;<!-- Δ --></mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>t</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msub>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle t=n\Delta _{t},f=m\Delta _{f},\tau =p\Delta _{t}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/3a42cd074689fc6025fa342679602703138de35a" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -1.005ex; width:27.884ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="{\displaystyle t=n\Delta _{t},f=m\Delta _{f},\tau =p\Delta _{t}}"></span></dd></dl>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle X(n\Delta _{t},m\Delta _{f})=\sum _{-\infty }^{\infty }w((n-p)\Delta _{t})x(p\Delta _{t})e^{-j2\pi pm\Delta _{t}\Delta _{f}}\Delta _{t}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <mi>X</mi>
