</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/436be28df652bed409c2456f073b5fa64b93888d" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.005ex; width:9.537ex; height:5.343ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \Delta _{t}&lt;{\frac {1}{2\Omega }}}"></span>, where <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \Omega }">
