<p>d. Only for implementing the <a href="/wiki/Rectangular_mask_short-time_Fourier_transform" title="Rectangular mask short-time Fourier transform">rectangular-STFT</a>
</p><p>Rectangular window imposes the constraint
</p>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle w((n-p)\Delta _{t})=1}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <mi>w</mi>
        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>
